               <msContents>
                  <summary>End of a private letter with farewell formula written in a second hand.  Several people send greetings including Dionysia, Hierax and the sister of the writer.  The recipient is asked to send a purple garment, sandals and perhaps boots</summary>
                  <msItem>
                     <note type="general">Written along the fibers; back blank</note>
                     <note type="general">8 lines; broken top and left?</note>
                     <note type="general">The hand is slowly written, with most letters formed separately, although some ligatures are used</note>
                     <textLang mainLang="grc">In Greek</textLang>
